:-)
this cant find my network driver :S

jangi: that's usually simple problem to fix. go to control panel->hardware and sound->device manager. there you will see the unit who is not functioning marjed with a yellow sign. click that device->properties->details and then scroll to "harware ids". there is a code there. google it. that's you missing driver.

And remember that drivers for Vista works on W7.
